          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Federal Travel Transparency Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires a federal executive agency to report additional information to the General Services Administration (GSA) regarding travel by the agency head or certain high-level officials compensated on the Executive Schedule. The GSA must make the information publicly available on a travel information website.</p>]]></text>
